Package: shapeshiftr
Title: Automated pipeline for shape manipulation and data transforms
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Lucas", "Khenayfis", , "lucaskhenayfus@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package intends to unify several kinds of data wrangling under a single framework.
    This includes shape manipulation as well data transformations. All is meant to be easily
    readable and extensible, aiming at greatly simplifying the process of data preparation before
    fitting/using models.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0),
Imports:
    data.table (>= 1.14.10),
    wavelets (>= 0.3)
Encoding: UTF-8
